{{fr-noun|m|-|+}}

# the man that is [[needed]] at a particular moment
#: {{uxi|fr|être l''''homme de la situation'''|to be the guy, to be the man that can [[solve]] the [[problem]], to be the man to do it, to be the [[right]] man for the job, to be the right man at the right time}}

====Usage notes====
* Almost only used in ''être l'homme de la situation''.
* The feminine equivalent is {{m|fr|femme de la situation}}.
* Not to be confused with {{m|fr|homme du moment}}.

